55
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:34,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ponovno, vaša je, po mom mišljenju, mnogo bolja, ali ćemo se pozabaviti tim.

56
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vrlo brzo.

57
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:50,879
