123
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je vaš način neuspjeha.

124
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,759
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ovo je moj način neuspjeha.

125
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:34,720
